<body is="base-page" id="page-landing">
<header>
      <h1>🖇 link link dot click</h1>
      <p class="emphasis">A simple tool for readers of the internet.</p>
      <form class="row responsive editable" method="post" action="/session">
        <label for="email">Login/Signup: </label>
        <input id="email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com">
        <button class="login" name="btn-login" type="submit" value="1">Go</button>
      </form>
</header>
  <main>
    <section>
      <p>Think of it as an <abbr title="RDF Site Summary or Really Simple Syndication">RSS</abbr>-enhanced blogroll. It's not rocket science, but it is handy:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔗 Add sites you want to check in on</li>
        <li>✨ Use RSS to see what's new</li>
        <li>📚 Sort based on when you last clicked</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Also:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>💅 Fun little <abbr title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS</abbr> editor</li>
        <li>☕️ JavaScript optional</li>
        <li>🧳 <abbr title="Outline Processor Markup Language (used by RSS readers + browser bookmarks)">OPML</abbr> import/export</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/demo">Try the demo</a>, or just sign up above 👆.</p>

    </section>
    {{ template "footer.html.tmpl" }}
  </main>
</body>